{
  "texts": [
    "Subsequently, we implement a filtering mechanism that excludes videos with short titles, low view counts, or absent hashtags.",
    "Furthermore, we discard videos with irrelevant hashtags such as \"YouTube,\" \"video,\" and \"shorts.\"",
    "Building on the annotations generated in Section 3.2, we further refine our selection by eliminating irrelevant videos, thus establishing a closed-loop data collection and iteration process.",
    "Ultimately, we curate a collection of 2,265 timelapse videos that meet our specified criteria.",
    "Cascade Preprocessing Due to complex scene transitions in Internet videos (see Fig. 2a) affecting the model's learning of temporal relevance, we need to find a way to solve this problem."
  ]
}